On behalf of BaptistCare, CBRE are pleased to offer 28 Memorial Avenue, Kellyville for sale.

The property boasts the following attributes:

• Zoned R3 Medium Density
• Concept scheme for 48 detached dwellings
• 20,230sqm (5 acres)*
• 500m* walk to proposed shopping centre
• North West Growth Centre and Bella Vista Station structure plan (Priority Precinct)
• Front exposure to proposed T-way along Memorial Avenue

1-1.5km approx. Radius: Norwest Business Park, Castle Hill Country Club, Bella Vista Station, Kellyville & Showground Stations and Kellyville Plaza.

The property will be sold via Expressions of Interest on Tuesday, 5th April at 3PM.

For further information, please do not hesitate to contact the listings agents.

CBRE and Matrix Property are pleased to present Lot 11 Windsor Road, Kellyville to the market for sale via Expressions of Interest closing Friday the 27th of March 2020 at 3:00pm (AEDT). This development site is a great opportunity and should not be overlooked as it has potential to provide revenue for the 2020 and 2021 financial year.

Lot 11 Windsor Road, Kellyville boasts the follow key attributes:
- DA Approved subdivision creating 53 lots/dwellings
- Some pre-sales and Integrated Housing Estate
- Site Area: 2.19Ha* (*Approx)
- R3 – Medium Density Residential

This Information Memorandum outlines the key attributes of the site. All information provided to interested parties is to assist in their preparation of independent Due Diligence.

Further information and inspection times are available upon request by contacting the exclusive agent

CBRE are pleased to offer an outstanding residential englobo development opportunity on behalf of the Deerubbin Local Aboriginal Land Council.

Lots 2002, 2003 & 2004 Saltwater Circle, has the potential to be subdivided into residential allotments, which are suitable for house and land packages.

Key features of the site include:
- Total site area: 6.22Ha* (15.41acres*)

- All services available for connection

- Close proximity to key amenities, including North Kellyville Square http://www.northkellyvillesquare.com.au/

This exciting residential development opportunity is for sale via Public Treaty.

CBRE as exclusive sales and marketing agents, are pleased to offer 2 Withers Road, Kellyville via Expression of Interest Campaign closing on Thursday the 7th of September at 3.00pm

The opportunity to purchase a raw parcel of R2 land is located in the heart of North West growth corridor is one not to be missed. This 5-acre parcel presents a vanilla house and land package development opportunity that is positioned moments from amenities including shopping and education.

Supported by the fastest delivery of transport infrastructure, business park employment growth and amenity development - Sydney’s North West has seen significant population growth and are only projected to further increase – all contributing to a healthy backbone to the house and land package market.

Opportunity highlights include;

- 20,260sqm* (5 acres) corner parcel fronting both Withers Road and Foxall Road, Kellyville
- Zoned R2 Low density residential
- 450m* to brand new retail and dining precinct at North Kellyville Square anchored by Woolworths
- 5min* drive to future Kellyville train station
